Package com.ecoguard.ecoguard.dto

Record Class DeviceStatusResponse

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.ecoguard.ecoguard.dto.DeviceStatusResponse
Record Components:
lastReadingTime - timestamp of the most recent sensor reading
temperature - latest temperature reading in degrees Celsius
humidity - latest humidity reading as a percentage
co2 - latest CO2 reading in ppm
lightLevel - latest light reading in lux
lastAlertTime - timestamp of the most recent alert
lastAlertType - type of the most recent alert (THRESHOLD or INTRUDER)
lastAdminMessage - text of the last DISPLAY_MESSAGE command sent
online - true if device is considered online (data received within 20 seconds)
secondsSinceLastSeen - number of seconds since last data was received
public record DeviceStatusResponse(LocalDateTime lastReadingTime, BigDecimal temperature, BigDecimal humidity, Integer co2, Integer lightLevel, LocalDateTime lastAlertTime, String lastAlertType, String lastAdminMessage, boolean online, Long secondsSinceLastSeen) extends Record
Data Transfer Object for device status information.

Contains comprehensive device status including latest sensor readings, online/offline status, last alert, and last admin message. Used by the admin panel's Device Status card.

Since:
1.0
